## Options (settings) page — `options/`

- **Files**: `options/options.html`, `options/options.css`, `options/options.js`. Logic lives in `OptionsManager` in `options.js`.
- **Layout**: Centered shell (~860px), **left sidebar** (~200px) for nav + footer (dark mode, privacy link, version). Main column holds section panels. Bottom bar: **Reset** + **Save** only; primary blue is reserved mainly for **Save** and focus/rings.
- **Navigation**: Buttons use `data-tab` values `api | languages | theme | cache | test` and target `#tab-{name}`. Active item: class **`is-active`** and **`aria-current="page"`** (styled in `options.css`, not ad-hoc Tailwind lists in JS).
- **Typography (options only)**: **Manrope** via Google Fonts (`options.html`). Weights: 400 body, 500 labels/sidebar, 600 section titles.
- **Dark mode**: `utils/dark-mode.js` binds **`#toggleDarkMode`** (sidebar footer on options).
- **API provider cards**: Radio cards use `.api-option-card` / `.api-option-radio`; inline status rows use `[data-status-for="mymemory|gemini|openrouter|both"]`. **`updateApiCardStatus()`** in `options.js` must stay in sync with key fields on input + after `populateForm`.
- **Theme tab**: Theme definitions in `utils/themes.js` (`PREDEFINED_THEMES`). Previews are built in **`renderThemeSelector()`** as **mini popup mocks** (`.theme-mini-*`) using each theme’s `colors` tokens (`background`, `border`, `headerBorder`, `text`, `textSecondary`, `translatedText`, `buttonBg`, `buttonText`). Caption under the preview uses `.theme-option-caption` (neutral page colors).
- **Tailwind on options**: `utils/tailwind.css` supplies utilities; **component layout and design tokens** for settings live in **`options.css`** (prefer adding new settings styles there).

Manifest and Permissions:

- Use the latest manifest version (v3) unless there is a specific need for v2
